    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines a YANG data module that can be used to configure and manage OSPF Segment Routing. It also defines a module for management of Signaling Maximum SID Depth (MSD) Using OSPF. The modules are based on YANG 1.1 as defined in RFC 7950 and conform to the Network Management Datastore Architecture (NDMA) as described in RFC 8342.</t>
